INSERT INTO "courses" VALUES(NULL,'SA 16 (cours semestriel)','Cours: Communication, organisation et e-Business','Course: Communication, organization and e-Business','Ce cours traite des volutions de la communication et des organisations lies au dveloppement des technologies de linformation et de la communication, et notamment dInternet. On rappellera les fondements thoriques permettant de cerner ces volutions et on examinera les nouvelles formes de mdiation qui se dveloppent avec les e-activits. Laccent sera mis sur les changements organisationnels et communicationnels dans le cadre du e-business. Les questions lies au e-marketing et  la cybercrise seront galement tudies.  This lecture analyses changes in communication and organizations related to the development of information and communication technology, more specifically Internet. Theoretical backgrounds which permit to understand these changes will be presented; then new forms of mediation which are developing with e-activities will be examined. We will insist on organizational and communicational changes in the framework of e-business. Questions related to e-marketing and cyber crisis will also be studied.','6640-1273','français','Bourgeois D.',NULL,'Master',2,3.0,'Objectifs du cours : ce cours a pour objectif de prsenter les grandes caractristiques des changements communicationnels et organisationnels, notamment lis  lessor dInternet et du e-business. Objectives of the course: this lecture aims at showing the main characteristics of the communicational and organizational changes, particularly linked to the development of Internet and e-business.',NULL,'chaque anne','Date Heure Cours / Excercice Salle Mardi 20.09.2016 15:15 - 17:00 Cours PER 21 B130 Mardi 27.09.2016 15:15 - 17:00 Cours PER 21 B130 Mardi 04.10.2016 15:15 - 17:00 Cours PER 21 B130 Mardi 11.10.2016 15:15 - 17:00 Cours PER 21 B130 Mardi 18.10.2016 15:15 - 17:00 Cours PER 21 B130 Mardi 25.10.2016 15:15 - 17:00 Cours PER 21 B130 Mardi 08.11.2016 15: